      "content": "tea or music... it just feels like distractions for people who don't understand. i'm not looking for a moment of peace, i'm looking for the end of this. it feels like i'm just waiting for my body to catch up with my heart. like, if he's gone, then the part of me that was actually alive is gone too. what am i supposed to do with a life that's already finished?",
